			Data Field: dfVarietyType
				Class Child Ref Key: 0
				Class ChildKey: 0
				Class: OurTblQBEDataField
				Property Template:
				Class DLL Name:
				Data
					Maximum Data Length: Default
					Data Type: Class Default
					Editable? Class Default
				Display Settings
